Yandex,is,the,largest,search,engine,in,Russia,and,develops,a,number,of,Internet,based,services,and,products,Yandex,offers,owners,of,websites,and,blogs,tools,with,which,they,can,apply,the,functional,services,of,Yandex,in,their,projects,The,site,and,documentation,are,in,Russian,The,Yandex,Maps,API,is,a,free,tool,that,allows,developers,to,embed,maps,on,their,website,Using,the,API,users,can,manage,cards,and,their,contents,as,well,as,create,a,variety,of,applications,from,simple,interactive,directions,to,the,office,to,advanced,GIS,services,The,API,uses,both,REST,and,JavaScript,protocol,and,returns,a,map,image,based,on,specified,parameters